additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: EACH TABLET CONTAINS: Globe artichoke (Cynara scolymus) extract equiv. fresh leaf 1 g STANDARDISED EXTRACTS EQUIVALENT TO DRY: Milk thistle (Silybum marianum extract 35.71 mg) equiv. dry fruit 2.5 g; Turmeric (Curcuma longa extract 75 mg) equiv. dry rhizome 1.5 g

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Do not use if pregnant or likely to become pregnant. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians.
